metadata.name: Yumiko
metadata.description:
This mysterious and alluring look took over my mind. 
I can't look away because I want to enjoy this beautiful girl. She's perfect and she'll never be with you, but you continue to love her and enjoy every minute of being with her...but unfortunately the moment will come when you will never see each other again...
The first strong love is very cruel

2950x4000pxl
Original artwork by CreepyPipo
